Noteworthy changes in version 0.3.1 (2022-04-07) [C1/A1/R2]
------------------------------------------------

 * Support ephemeral ECDSA cipher suites. [rT08c1622944]

 * Do not install ntbtls-config if the new gpgrt-config is available.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.3.0 (2022-02-07) [C1/A1/R1]
------------------------------------------------

 * Support for X448 and X25519 when build with Libgcrypt 1.9 or later.

 * Updates to the build system.

 * Build fixes for macOS.  [T5440,T5601]


Noteworthy changes in version 0.2.0 (2020-08-27) [C1/A1/R0]
------------------------------------------------

 * Add support for ciphersuites using GCM.

 * New function to return alert messages.

 * Improvements to the build system.

 * Interface changes relative to version 0.1.2
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   ntbtls_get_last_alert           NEW function.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.1.2 (2017-09-19) [C0/A0/R2]
------------------------------------------------

 * Add support for secp384r1, secp521r1, and 3 Brainpool curves.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.1.1 (2017-03-16) [C0/A0/R1]
------------------------------------------------

 * Now supports ECDHE-RSA key exchange.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.1.0 (2017-02-21) [C0/A0/R0]
------------------------------------------------

 * Initial experimental release with only the client code.


